{"word":"H488 - אַלְמָן - ʼalmân - al-mawn' - Forsaken","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַלְמָן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼalmân"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>al-mawn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Forsaken"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கைவிடப்பட்ட, விதவை - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"widowed, forsaken, forsaken as a widow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Prolonged from <a href=\"#/H481 - אָלַם - ʼâlam - aw-lam'/481\">H481</a> in the sense of <i>bereavement</i>; discarded (as a divorced person): - forsaken."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H480 - אַלְלַי - ʼalᵉlay - al-le-lah'ee/480\">H480</a>, <a href=\"#/H481 - אָלַם - ʼâlam - aw-lam'/481\">H481</a>, <a href=\"#/H482 - אֵלֶם - ʼêlem - ay'-lem/482\">H482</a>, <a href=\"#/H483 - אִלֵּם - ʼillêm - il-lame'/483\">H483</a>, <a href=\"#/H485 - אֲלֻמָּה - ʼălummâh - al-oom-maw'/485\">H485</a>, <a href=\"#/H488 - אַלְמָן - ʼalmân - al-mawn'/488\">H488</a>, <a href=\"#/H489 - אַלְמֹן - ʼalmôn - al-mone'/489\">H489</a>, <a href=\"#/H490 - אַלְמָנָה - ʼalmânâh - al-maw-naw'/490\">H490</a>, <a href=\"#/H491 - אַלְמָנוּת - ʼalmânûwth - al-maw-nooth'/491\">H491</a>, <a href=\"#/H492 - אַלְמֹנִי - ʼalmônîy - al-mo-nee'/492\">H492</a>, <a href=\"#/H495 - אֶלָּסָר - ʼEllâçâr - el-law-sawr'/495\">H495</a>"}]}